<p id="L298">――ピッ</p>
<p id="L299"><br></p>
<p id="L300">「ああああああああああああああああああああああ！！」</p>
<p id="L301"><br></p>
<p id="L302"><a href="//46053.mitemin.net/i1016907/" target="_blank"><img src="//46053.mitemin.net/userpageimage/viewimagebig/icode/i1016907/" alt="挿絵(By みてみん)" border="0"></a></p>
<p id="L303"><br></p>
<p id="L304">（ごめん……ごめんね、サラ……！</p>
